---
title: Fiery Gochujang Tofu Noodles with garlicky green beans
description: Gochujang paste is a savoury, sweet, and spicy fermented condiment used widely in Korean cuisine. Made from chilli peppers, it's known to pack a punch! In this dish, it coats egg noodles and Thai Spiced tofu for a tongue-tingling meal that comes together quickly.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R21_W15_IE_IEXQVV17476-7_Main__4high-ba9bb498.jpg
